                        "- **Choose availability (AP)**: the system **keeps accepting reads even though it may return stale data**, and `n1`/`n2` **keep accepting writes**; data is **synced to `n3` once the partition is resolved** (p. 92).\n"
                        "\n"
                        "## Interview takeaway\n"
