                        "Download = notification (or offline cache) -> fetch metadata -> download blocks -> reconstruct file.",
                        "Long polling is chosen over WebSocket because notifications are one-directional and infrequent.",
                        "Save space via block dedup (by hash), version limits, and cold storage (S3 Glacier); handle failures with replication and failover.",
